author: Briana Hansen
title: 15 confessions from ultra competitive couples
text:
15 confessions from ultra competitive couples It’s nice to date someone with ambition. And being in a relationship with a person who inspires you to do better is really good for you. But some people like to compete with the person they date . Sometimes it can get a little overboard. But often, it’s just fun and adorable ways to bond with a significant other.
So here are some confessions of people who are in very competitive relationships. Whether it’s to make the other laugh or to get the final word, these couples share just what it’s like to be involved this kind of partnership. These confessions are courtesy of Whisper .
